{"tid":874640,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"林太山莊兩房劈「1球」易手 回到去年底","createTime":"2018-10-24T10:45:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-25T02:33:02.000Z","uid":22839,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"d41f17c09befc1e3f1a58a4abb278b3519ba852f","tid":874640,"uid":22839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T10:45:01.000Z","msg":"專家食屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n二手樓劈價盤湧現，部份買家由新盤轉投二手。利嘉閣陳嘉興表示，天水圍嘉湖山莊再錄「四字頭」成交，為樂湖居7座中層F室，實用面積449方呎，兩房間隔，原叫價480萬元，放盤短短兩天以開價售出，呎價10,690元。新買家曾入票認購新盤，惟樓花期長，二手樓價又跌了，最終決定買二手樓，可即買即住。<br />\n同座高層E室，實用面積448方呎，今年7月以高達575萬元成交，呎價12,835元，與最新造價比較，<span style=\"color: red;\">短短3個月跌價接近100萬元，跌幅16.5%。而樂湖居4座高層E室於去年10月以475萬元沽出，意味今次造價已重返去年底水平。</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n受業主減價刺激，嘉湖山莊本月暫錄得近20宗成交，已超越上月全月約16宗，大部份屬減價成交，減幅10%至13%。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20181024/58830434\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181024%2F58830434&d=oV03Jz3tVDaVEDGqvmAcKMVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=694bf02b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181024%2F58830434&h=f1038548\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20181024/58830434</a>"},{"pid":"92b22e2a0d7b2fd059551d9cf30d7398854cfeef","tid":874640,"uid":104965,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T10:59:27.000Z","msg":"呢d 大西北地區 3球2房我都係貴<br />\n不如住租深圳住 香港返工唔好？"},{"pid":"820226207d32141faad28fbc0ecc84d8bb1d202e","tid":874640,"uid":1067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T11:01:59.000Z","msg":"林太開始蝕錢未？"},{"pid":"47f9f86cb583c2b4e66ad38eb259306a834f7474","tid":874640,"uid":62935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"82022620